<project>
	<extend>${defaults.xml}</extend>
	<id>backend</id>
	<name>E-CAS Backend</name>
	<currentVersion>0.0.0</currentVersion>
	<shortDescription>EDRN Catalog/Archive Backend</shortDescription>
	<description>
		The Early Detection Research Network (EDRN) deploys a Catalog and Archive Service (CAS) known
		as E-CAS.  E-CAS comes in two parts: a web-based user interface and a backend storage system.
		This component is the backend storage system.  It provides authenticated XML-RPC-based
		interfaces for both the user interface as well as for programs (such as ingest scripts) to
		manipulate the catalog/archive.
	</description>
